content.detailedDescription: Walked out patio and noticed what i thought was a huge star. it was very big and bright but realized it wasn't a star when it started moving. it moved very slow! didn't hear anything only train that is close to my house. like it covered a lot of area as it traveled in what seemed like a straight path but it moved so slow almost memorizing i couldn't stop watching. i video taped some of it and happy i did because when i watched the video i zoomed in and u can tell through video that it is disc shaped and the lights seem to go around and around on the object. when i look back at watching it in real time though it just looked like a big star. only white lights no red or green like on helicopters and airplanes. whatch video
content.summary: Walked out patio and noticed what i thought was a huge star. it was very big and bright but realized it wasn't a star when it started moving

content.detailedDescription: We were driving south on interstate 25 and we noticed a giant ball of fire flashing. it seemed like it was like a light flashing on and off, but it was a fire type light. i have seen meteors on the internet and in the sky before and this was not a meteor. the ufo was slowly gliding next to us about 100-500 feet away in the sky. i could see it clearly through the front windshield. it was flying sideways next to us slowly and kept on flashing on and off. it was a like a fire in the sky, but a fireball. on the same trip we witnessed a giant 4-5 foot owl standing in the middle of the highway i had to swerve to avoid it. the owl seemed like it just appeared out of nowhere right in front of us on the road. it stared at us with no fear of our oncoming vehicle towards it. it really scared the heck out of me. i will never forget this.
content.summary: Flashing fireball shaped ufo

content.detailedDescription: I was driving to my boss's house to pickup a couch he was giving me i stopped at a red light and i noticed the clouds abruptly they clearly looked as if large ships were protruding from them as if being purposely shrouded. i was shocked i looked at the guy in the car next to me and pointed and he looked and nodded like he realized too. it was a strange feeling i felt like i could tell something wasn't right right with the clouds so i tried to take a few pictures there were at least two of these clouds with the ships protruding clearly visible and possibly many more just being hidden better it was tough to get a good shot of it somehow and the light turned green so i went but felt odd all day. i remember it was a really calm morning and a gust of wind had just kicked up like a passing front i thought maybe this blew some of the ships cloud cover away leaving them partially exposed.
content.summary: Large ufo/ufos protruding from clouds

content.summary: Very bright light in upper northern sky. light became even brighter then slowly turned into black.

content.detailedDescription:
At my ranch in near meridian, rural central texas, i have several ( 8 total)  trail cams set out at my various deer feeders. i periodically retrieve the sd cards and check the pics. 
while checking all my cam pics last weekend, i saw that on one of my cams, on july 22 from 4-6 am, among all the other pics taken on it, took 4 nighttime infrared pics of a feeder with a concentrated, very focused  beam of light shining down from somewhere above and off to the side of the feeder, shining at the ground at a slight angle. the first 3 pics have the beam shining at deer, the last pic shows the beam of light but has no animals in it. the beam of light even shows to have lens flares. 
unless there is a defect in the camera on these 4 pics, which i hope someone can show me, i otherwise cannot explain. 
last year i had a similar set of pics. only these had some hexagonal shimmering lighted shape appear at the top of the frame with a less focused beam of light shining down on a feeder. again, about 3-4 am. 
only w helicopter could hover and shine a spotlight down onto my place. but none have been sighted and there is no reason for one being at my place. 
i am willing to have my cameras checked.
content.summary: Trail cam pics at my ranch show beams of light shining down on animals at a deer feeder at 4-6 am.

content.detailedDescription: ,my name jim i am 53 years old native american. i have seen ufo's through out my life in total i have to many sighting too count.My first encounter was in the early evening in 1975 three lead metal color flying in formation.They were 80 feet above my head they were 30 of us that saw it.I just wanted you too know that there is a lot of activity here in lethbridge i have seen six ufo's in the last three days . has anyone else contacted you about any sighting in alberta?.
content.summary: Saw a flash then seen the two lights one was a helicopter trying to keep up with it but flew after it till it was out of sight

content.detailedDescription: While camping in hays state park we sitting at the fire when we noticed a bright red light coming from the south ascending slowly. the object was red with a yellow inner glow. it almost looked like a chinese lantern that was on fire or had a candle burning inside of it the way the light flickered. we were sitting in a stand of trees. as the object got closer it got higher and went up over the tree line. we followed it with our eyes as it headed north continuing over the trees. once it had cleared our campground it was out of our line of sight.  the whole event took less than 2 minutes start to finish. it never made any noise. and we tried to get other campers around us to observe it. the sky was completely clear and you could see airplanes in the distance. it was frightening at first as it was coming towards us. i almost thought it would get caught in the trees.
content.summary: Observed object rising above trees coming towards us, flew over made no sound and continued gaining altitude while traveling northerly.

content.detailedDescription:
While camping on perdido key, a primitive campground on july 6 ,a few miles from pensacola naval air station, around 11:30p.M., i saw a round craft with red lights go out into the bay with search lights on the ground following it. it went to a spot 200-300 feet in the air, it hovered then circled back to the airstrip. this happened 4-5 times. i had my binoculars and was only 2-3 miles from it. when it landed, from what i could see, it seemed a cloud of gas or fog? surrounded the object. i got the feeling it was remote controlled because on one of the flights while hovering it bounced up and down while hovering like someone was having some with a joystick.
 in summing it up; it took off, hovered at the same spot and returned to the area it took off from which was the airbase over the course of a half of an hour 4-5 times.
content.summary: A circular object took off from pensacola nas. round with red lights. it hovered for a few minutes and landed back on the nas.

content.detailedDescription:
My wife & i were parked on a side street watching the fireworks at the ridgecrest fairgrounds one mile to our s/e. at aprox. 9:10pm my wife & i both saw a definate blue streak going up to aprox 1,000ft.Off my left shoulder to the east. as the blue streak vanished a star like object remained. i then looked at my wife & said, did you see that, she replied yes. she watched the object with me for aprox 60 sec. then turned to watch the fireworks. aprox. 3 min. later the object began to move slowly in a s/e direction towards the fireworks. it continued to slightly gain alt. to aprox. 2,000 and the stopped & hovered one mile east of the fairgrounds. my wife was again looking at the object & i jokenly said, " i guess our visitors like to watch the fireworks too. " my wife not being a fan of the ufo subject matter shrugged off my comment & continued to watch the fireworks.
i watched the object & at aprox. 9:20 the object slowly moved off to the s/e gaining alt. its angle of assent increased and so did the speed and the starlike object became smaller & smaller until it dissapeared in the s/e direction. my first thought was that the object was a personal drone however the last distance & speed ruled that out. it was also definately not a helecopter. the first blue light was solid with no sparks and i instantly ruled out fireworks.
content.summary: Began as a blue streak going up. then hovered as a star. then moved on to s/e elevated.

content.detailedDescription:
Hey all.. this is my first time posting, long time follower of mufon reports.

im a photographer in the greater philadelphia area (langhorne, bucks county) that likes to point my lens towards the cosmos and snap slow exposures of the night time sky.  its become a fun little hobby for me over the years.  

recently, on july 15th 2016 at approximately 9:15pm i set my nikon d90 on a tripod and pointed towards the sw sky..  set the camera for 30 second exposures while on the tripod for maximum light and clarity.  no movement is optimum.  after snapping 4-5 similar shots in the front yard towards the sw, i repeated the same process stated above, except i went in my backyard and pointed my nikon towards the ne and snapped 4-5 of the same 30 second slow exposure shots of the night sky.

i really don't have much more information than what i have included.  when shooting the set of photos i had captured, nothing seemed different or weird when i was shooting.

that said, after shooting the photos i mentioned, i came in and started to look thru and see how the stars & planets looked in the night sky.  most of the photos came out like they usually do, but 2 really stood out to me.. because there was things after the fact while looking at the captures on my computer that i noticed some things. 

photo 1 in my front yard is facing sw has a spiral - tri-spoked - greenish looking orb bright in the sky..  maybe some type of weird light reflection

photo 2 is in my back yard and facing towards the ne.. this 2nd photo has a bunch more preset orbs, streaks or 'swooshes' of light and a very obvious cigar shaped 'object'.. 

like i said, maybe weird glitch in the system or weird refracted light - but yea - not sure.. 

any how.  thanks in advance for your time.
content.summary: Night sky photography with peculiar orbs and shapes

content.detailedDescription:
Two white craft and many orbs


saturday sept. 19, 2015 i had been noticing some momentary objects in just fractions of a second.  so i decided to take a series of four videos beginning at 12:30 dst.  in the fourth one which lasted 12 seconds, i caught a light grey orb moving.  on a whim, i decided to take a couple photos from the front of the house over a tower in our area.   

however, about an hour later i saw two white craft outside of our bedroom window.  i ran to the living room and grabbed the camera and recorded a fifth video.  a lot of activity was going on i was to discover.  this fifth video lasted 51 seconds.  the lower of the two craft turned out to be a small piper type of plane.  but what was following it from above was completely something else!!

the sequence of events was:
1.	at 12:30 pm dst i took four random videos.  videos 1-3 had nothing of interest. but video 4 did.
2.	at 12:36 pm dst i took a photo of the tower out front out of curiosity.
3.	at 13:29 pm dst i saw 2 white craft out back, and took the fifth video.
4.	at 13:32 pm dst i wondered if the craft were still visible out front of the house, and took a photo of the plane.

two white craft (the 5th video):
shot at 13:29 dst and toward the nnw (346°) this video caught two white craft in the air at about 30° altitude. note that to the left and upper part of the image of frame 43:14 with the arrow, there is a small dark sphere following the uppermost white craft.  in the next image in frame 46:27, there is also a dark sphere below it.

a still photo entitled “plane with dark orb”, taken at 13:32 dst roughly at 90° is of the same plane in the far left of the image, but with a dark orb-like object to the far right in the photo that was following it from the front of the house.  the image entitled “detail of orb” shows as much as could be enhanced of the orb.

 two edited images entitled “frame 36:45” and “frame 43:26” show more of the detail of the white craft that was following the airplane.  at times the craft seemed to lengthen.  at other times it was not in two pieces but a single white craft.  since a piper type aircraft is 22 feet long, and the craft following the plane was 60% of it’s size, this makes the craft 13 feet in length.
               
photo of tower:
at 12:36 dst an image entitled “tower w 18 orbs” was taken at 96° (east), and after working to enhance the photo, and inverting the colors, shows at least 18 dark orb-like craft around it.

from the 4th video:
at 12:33 dst, the 4th video shot at 346° (nnw) caught some dark orbs in frames 
:00, :06, and frame :19.  the image “photomerge of orb motion” is a merging of three frames and shows how the orb travelled in 1/3 of a second making an angular direction change of 50° in 20/60 of a second.

the image of the orb was the clearest in frame :19 and has been cropped and enhanced entitled “enhanced orb”.

summary:
1.	at least one dark orb was seen during the shooting of the 4th video at 12:33 dst in the nnw.  it was seen travelling very rapidly through the viewfinder in 1/3 of a second, making an abrupt directional change of 50° straight toward the zenith.
2.	three minutes later, at 12:36 dst at 90° (east), at least 18 different dark orbs are seen surrounding the tower.
3.	an hour later at 13:29 dst, at 346° (nnw), the 5th video of the two white craft shows that one was an airplane, and the other is an unknown uav which seemed to be stalking it, that was 13 feet long.
4.	in addition to the white craft, two small dark orbs can be seen surrounding the white craft. 
5.	a total of at least 22 craft were seen over the span of an hour.
6.	case 76946 (full spectrum camera images) was shot on the same day, about an hour after the last image in this report.  four craft were seen in that report.  thus in the span of two hours that day, 26 craft were filmed and reported.
content.summary: I saw a white craft following a piper type of plane, then many small dark orbs.

content.detailedDescription:
I observed the object after i got home and was looking through some pictures i had taken earlier that day.  i did not observe the object with the naked eye.
the pictures i took were late in the morning of 7-25-2016.

i was at an observation point in brownington vermont, high on a hill taking random pictures with my 20.1 megapixel nikon koolpix. it is a mountainous, forested area. the picture in which the object appears was taken facing north towards lake memphremagog. i did not see the object when i took the picture, and other pictures that i took of the same area and at the same time do not show the object.

the day was cloudy and overcast but not raining or foggy.  temperature was about 83 f, fairly humid, and  light breeze.

i brought my camera home with me after i left the area, about a 40 minute drive.  when i got home i hooked the camera into my laptop to look at the pictures i had taken. it was at that time that i discovered the photo with the object in the upper left hand corner of the shot. 

i would estimate that i was about 10 miles away from the lake that appears in the photo.  there is a small airport to the left of the area that appears in the photo, also about 10 miles away.  i did not observe or hear any aircraft during the time i was taking pictures.  i did not see any birds when i was taking pictures.

my initial reaction to seeing the object in the photo was that it was a bird or an airplane that had somehow gotten into the shot.  but as i looked more closely at the object in the photo, and zoomed in on it with various magnifications, it did not appear to be either a bird or a plane. but i could tell that it appeared to be a solid object of some kind in the distance.  again, i did not see the object with the naked eye, but only when i got home and was looking through the photos i had taken.

i certainly have no interest perpetrating a fraud by sending you this photo and information.  i would just like to get an informed opinion as to what the object in the picture could be.  if you have any questions or need any further information please do not hesitate to contact me.

i was not sure how to fill out some of this reporting form since i did not see the object with the naked eye, but only by observing a photo that i had taken earlier.

thank you for your time and consideration.
content.summary: Discovered object when observing a photo that i had taken earlier

content.detailedDescription: Bad clouds were moving in.Had a storm moving in so went outside on my back porch to take pictures of the sky..Took about 3 quick pics due to rain starting to come down.The last pic i took i seen them in the screen as i snapped the shot and i knew i seen something move really fast so i reviewed my pic and sure enough there tbey were.Couldnt believe what i captured at first.But i have caught other ufos in pictures also.Which i have too
content.summary: Looked like 5 disks appeared then disappeared just as fast

content.detailedDescription: I was on my balcony with my mother and i just like always was looking at the sky because space fascinates me. i saw 4 lights, i first thought they were airplanes or space junk but all airplanes have white and red lights and they blink, this one didnt blink and seemed too high for an airplane. space junk leaves behind trails when burning in the atmosphere and this didn't leave any trails. after approx. 20 seconds 3 of them disappeared slowly, like they noticed me and my mom looking at them. their lights slowly faded away and i couldn't see them anymor3 ( there were no clouds in the sky ). one of them remained in my sight and flew west. it disappeared goo but then i noticed a brighter light in the sky blinking three times (once every minute). and after that every light was gone. i was amazed because i always wanted to know what it felt like to witness something like this but a few minutes later a weird uncomfortable feeling hit me and didn't leave me for 10 minutes. it's still the only thing i can think about and what i find weird but this is probably just a coincidence, is that i was searching for exposed cia projects (stargate, mk ultra etc) earlier that day just for fun. and this past couple of days i was joking with my sister saying that i saw an ufo.
content.summary: Group of 4 lights. 3 faded away few seconds after "discovery". 1 flew to the west and blinked 3 times and disappeared.

content.detailedDescription: While driving on county route 7 (albany post road)south then west near the shawangunk fire house and small restaurant i witnessed a rectangular / elongated well lit object fly in a westerly direction.  it was several meters in front of me while i was driving my car. the object was flying in a relatively straight course.  as i rounded a bend in the road i saw the back of the object as it eventually flew over trees on the right side of the road and became obscured. the object was heading west toward the shawangunk mountain range.   the object was flying just above utility poles and i could see the silhouette of the telephone pole top against the bright side of the object that was facing me. the object did not produce any sound.
content.summary: Retangular/elongated object, well lite flew over sited area near shawangunk fire department on albany post road (also: county route 7near new paltz ny

content.detailedDescription: I never reported ufo events, i have seen in numerous occasions different types but the recent one was the following, i was getting ready that morning to head outdoors, i was in my room and turned around toward the window, for i felt this eery feeling that i had to look out and up toward the sky and there it was hovering over manhattan across the east river from where i live in a 7th floor building. white egg like shape ,in few seconds, created a tornado like grey cloud and less than a second disappeared through the tornado like cloud. something else happened days after, which was this saturday night, 23rd or 24th mid night. i have markings that are related to incidents of obstructions or was it done in my room. i question myself?
content.summary: Hoovered over manhattan, accross the east river from where i live. i live in a building 7th floor, day light morning. it hovers few seconds, created a grey tornado like cloud  and disappeared through it in less than a second. it happened so fast.

content.detailedDescription: My son and (and my daughter was in the house may also have seen it) was sitting on the back porch of our house in melville li in (late?) august  2007 at night (after sundown  - it was dark). he happened to notice 2 bright bluish lights hovering above him as he sat. he believes the lights were under a triangular object. but it was black and hard to see. it was still and probably 100 or more feet up. he decided to take out his flip phone and take pictures. he took 6 pictures in all but mainly you can only see the two lights. i tried to enhance them but with not much luck. but i am attaching them anyway. the last two pictures are the ones that are smaller as it is ascending straight up and out of sight. normally during the day small aircraft are allowed to fly over our area but not at night. i called the farmingdale airport to report a craft may have been  flying in a restricted area/time and asked them if they had anything on radar. they said that they had not seen anything on radar (we are only about 3 miles from the airport). i tried to enhance them at one point for more detail. it was so long ago i don't even know if these are the enhanced ones or copies of the originals (the dates on the file are from nov 2007 and are not the original times from august so they are at least copies). these look to me more like the original un-enhanced images because i remember when i enhanced them digitally it seemed a triangular shape became fairly evident. but here are the images. i was in the process of reporting a few (past) sightings of my own (for the record) so i thought i might as well throw this in!  you may have better enhancement techniques. the first 4 pictures are of a similar view / distance (pix 1 thru 4) so you may be able to get something by overlaying the images etc....    best luck - i put down that there were two witnesses because my daughter was in the house and i think my son called her out to see it and i seem to remember she also saw it. this whole thing lasted only a few minutes.
content.summary: My son noticed 2 lights under a black triangle hovering still above him while sitting on the back porch of house on night august 2007 - he took 6 flip phone pix and it asceded straight up until not visible

content.detailedDescription: It was approx 3am on a warm clear night when i woke up and went out on my back deck to have a smoke. i stood at the end of my deck and witnessed 6 to 8 light's flying silently approx 300-500 feet from the ground all in a straight line. they appeared to be all attached to one object.Approx a football field in length. i watched it silently fly away from me traveling west. i decided to reach for my phone and tried to record the lights but they were to far for the camera to record. i left my phone recording incase any thing else appeared. moments layer i witnessed another object flying at a much higher elevation and east across the sky.  i began recording it when i noticed a second object not far behind the first object at a even higher elevation. to high for the camera on my phone to record. about 5 minutes into the recording 2 more object flu past at extremely fast rates one north to south the other oppl site south to north. they were so fast they appeared to be streaks but we're much lower. almost as low as the first ufo i witnessed 300-500 feet from the ground. i was so shocked and excited i spent the rest of the twilight hours on my deck hoping to witness more. however nothing more happened.
content.summary: One ufo had 6 to 8 light's and was as low as the mountains tins the other 4 were much faster and higher in the sky

content.detailedDescription: Driving to buffalo eastbound on the i90. at approximately 1:30am about 10 to 15 miles outside the city, a bright light appeared in the eastern sky and streaked rapidly downward and disappeared. i was talking to a family member through my vehicles audio system when it occurred and i was very surprised to see it so clearly. upon further investigation, there have been several recent reports in buffalo the past two months of fireball type ufos being seen in various parts of the city. the whole encounter lasted under 3 seconds, and the object was moving extremely fast.
content.summary: Bright flash of light that streaked across eastern sky lasting 3 seconds

content.detailedDescription:
I was riding on the loveland bike trail from anderson to loveland.  it was just after 8:00 pm, and i was 3 hours into my trip.  i had another hour ahead of me, so i stopped to rest in the grass in milford.  

i was looking up in the sky and saw a barely visible white dot in the sky.  at first i thought it must be a jet, but it was way, way too high for a jet.  plus, it wasn't moving. 

it looked to be so high up that i began to wonder if it was the space station.  so i called my son and asked him to google where the space station was at that time, and he said it was over ukraine.  so clearly it wasn't the space station.  

the brightness of the light kept changing.  sometimes it seemed to be rhythmically getting light and dark. other times it seemed random.  sometimes it seemed both -- as though it might be simultaneously rotating, but  also having a flashing light on it.  the light that was flashing seemed white.  yet at other moments it seemed it could be red.  but, to be honest, it was so high in the sky i couldn't be sure.  

i watched it for 15 minutes, and it did seem to move during that time.  but, then, i though that the movement was so slow that it could just be that the earth was rotating in that time so that it appeared to be in a different place.  

i took a few photos of it, but it didn't show up in the photos because it was a flip phone and the camera was bad.  that, or it was simply too small to be captured.  

i have no idea as to whether satellites can be seen, but i just imagined that this was so high in the sky that it had to be a large object.  keep in mind, it was only 8:00 pm, and the sun was still bright.  so i'm sure that i was seeing the object itself --- not just light being emitted from it.  

after 15 minutes i had to get back on my bike and leave.

content.detailedDescription:
I was teaching a camp at the school where i work. i was taking the students out for recess when one of the kids ran up to me asking what those things in the sky were. he pointed to the north and i saw five objects flying. they were in formation, and started to move faster when i saw them. at first sight, i thought they might be helicopters, but i didn't see any chopper blades, and they were really bright. 

they were reflecting sunlight, looked like they were chrome. from my distance, they looked spherical. they were moving north east. as the formation moved, some of the individual orbs were moving back and forth quickly.

i was in complete shock. i tried to get my phone out to take a picture, but i didn't have time before they passed behind the school building out of my vantage point.
content.summary: Saw five objects flying in the sky in formation, moving back and forth in the formation
